{
  "3128530": {
    "name": "萍城异闻录 (Ping City)",
    "steam_appid": 3128530,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >这是一款二次元画质搭配快节奏热血战斗，《萍城异闻录》重构 ARPG 竞技新体验！指尖连招丝滑衔接，普攻、技能无缝 Combo，搭配火、水、雷等元素融合机制，轻松打出全屏高额伤害，战斗爽感拉满。<br><br><strong>创新玩法，告别传统套路</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >颠覆 “搜打撤” 模式：场内物资上传即锁定归属，无需撤离即可继续狩猎其他玩家，掠夺海量资源，竞技快感翻倍。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单局助战羁绊：收集金币解锁助战阵容，角色间触发专属羁绊，叠加强力增益 buff，策略搭配决定战局走向。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由魂卡体系：场景内搜集伤害、辅助、功能型三类魂卡，百种组合方式打造专属战斗流派，每局都有新体验。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自由生态，搬砖无压力</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >内置开放交易行系统，副本掉落、掠夺物资均可自由定价交易，轻松实现 “搬砖变现”。无绑定限制，珍品道具秒上架秒流通，平民玩家也能靠策略与肝度实现资源自由。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单局中商店可随机刷新助战英雄，玩家通过击杀怪物获得金币，购买助战英雄以获得英雄之力，几十种不同的阵容搭配，带给玩家惊喜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8种元素同台竞技，相互元素融合，组合成多元化的伤害效果，值得发掘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >羁绊系统，深化阵容搭配重要性。专属的助战英雄，触发强力的羁绊效果，产生多重打击特效，创意成就感强。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >躲猫猫，变身系统可躲避追踪，暗算敌对玩家，并增加趣味性操作空间，战斗过程其乐无穷。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【助战连携羁绊】</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中，随时可以招募助战角色，与你的主战角色形成搭配，触发超强合体技。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >英雄之间，互有羁绊效果，组建适合的阵容，触发羁绊效果，使战斗更有深度和养成性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128530/extras/f82a98024ea7757082a4f326bfb396b1.poster.avif?t=1770196583\" width=612 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128530/extras/f82a98024ea7757082a4f326bfb396b1.webm?t=1770196583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128530/extras/f82a98024ea7757082a4f326bfb396b1.mp4?t=1770196583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【魂卡】</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巧用魂卡触发融合伤害，攻防进退间皆是制胜关键！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操作方式：鼠标右键呼出轮盘，左键点击即可使用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >畅享酣畅淋漓的战斗快感！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128530/extras/c65020296fb9d25672d8d2d807681463.poster.avif?t=1770196583\" width=612 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128530/extras/c65020296fb9d25672d8d2d807681463.webm?t=1770196583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【搜索·战斗·上传】</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搜索宝箱、瓦罐等容器，夺取高价值物资！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掠夺之时，务必警惕周边虎视眈眈的敌人，随时准备战斗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >携所有物资前往指定上传点，坚守区域直至上传完成，战利品将即刻存入你的仓库！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128530/extras/736cd59b50be0c09b17227bad1e35aa1.poster.avif?t=1770196583\" width=612 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128530/extras/736cd59b50be0c09b17227bad1e35aa1.webm?t=1770196583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128530/extras/736cd59b50be0c09b17227bad1e35aa1.mp4?t=1770196583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【躲猫猫】</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >添加了躲猫猫系统，你可以在场景内，变成各式各样的形态，以躲避其他玩家的追踪，或者暗算其他玩家，又或者为自己提供一个安全的环境，来查询助战英雄。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128530/extras/b3112769f37a43e101e2e141157f2abd.poster.avif?t=1770196583\" width=612 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128530/extras/b3112769f37a43e101e2e141157f2abd.webm?t=1770196583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128530/extras/b3112769f37a43e101e2e141157f2abd.mp4?t=1770196583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【元素反应】</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏拥有8种元素伤害，除了物理以外的7种元素互相产生元素反应，不同的元素反应，为目标带来不同的负面效果，这也影响到了你的阵容选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128530/extras/2f3554bf60838293751e41c142fbbd0a.poster.avif?t=1770196583\" width=612 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128530/extras/2f3554bf60838293751e41c142fbbd0a.webm?t=1770196583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128530/extras/2f3554bf60838293751e41c142fbbd0a.mp4?t=1770196583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【大魔王】</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中，你可以通过击败场景中的龙兽，获得龙魂，龙魂会让你化身为大魔王，伤害变高，但同时也会让你受到更高的伤害，此时你会变成场上最显眼的那一个。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128530/extras/2d4940694c445868d9e4f3fc5133d055.poster.avif?t=1770196583\" width=612 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128530/extras/2d4940694c445868d9e4f3fc5133d055.webm?t=1770196583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128530/extras/2d4940694c445868d9e4f3fc5133d055.mp4?t=1770196583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【闪避、格挡、浮空追击、轻功】</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗包含了多样化的行为方式，灵活的使用他们，成为战斗大师吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128530/extras/5ba8833875a036fa08fa3e287f021bcd.poster.avif?t=1770196583\" width=612 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128530/extras/5ba8833875a036fa08fa3e287f021bcd.webm?t=1770196583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【丰富的PVE内容】</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >已完成了大量的PVE内容：组队大世界狩猎、单人闯关、深渊挑战、家园种植采集等等，将在未来与大家见面。</p>",
